author: Lauren Moraski CBS News
title: ​Ryan Sweeting requesting spousal support from Kaley Cuoco
text:
Ryan Sweeting is requesting spousal support from Kaley Cuoco in the wake of their divorce , according to court documents obtained by ET .
At $45 million, the "The Big Bang Theory " actress has a lot more net worth -- compared with Sweeting's reported $2 million.
27 Photos Splits Breaking up is hard to do, especially when you're in the public eye
Last month, Cuoco filed for divorce from the tennis player, citing irreconcilable differences. The former couple, who were married for 20 months, had a prenuptial agreement .
Cuoco and Sweeting, both 29, married in a New Year's Eve ceremony in 2013. They have no children together.
Cuoco's publicist said that the couple had mutually agreed to end their marriage.
"Kaley Cuoco and Ryan Sweeting have mutually decided to end their marriage," Cuoco's rep said. "They ask for privacy at this time. No further statement will be issued regarding this matter."
